          "url": "https://www.coindesk.com/business/2026/04/20/bitmine-buys-101-627-ether-worth-over-usd230-million-its-largest-weekly-haul-of-2026",
          "title": "Bitmine 買入 10 萬顆以太幣，價值逾 2.3 億美元，2026 年最大單週買入",
